  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell creates an invisible 20-foot diameter spherical barrier around the caster that repels all types of vermin, including insects, arachnids and rodents. Vermin with less than one-third the caster's level in HD cannot penetrate the barrier. Vermin with at least one-third the caster's level in HD can penetrate the barrier if they make a wisdom saving throw. Even so, vermin that cross the barrier suffer 1d6 points of damage.</p>",
